  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <p>PUT IT INTO PRACTICE:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Log into the admin dashboard and go to Users > Add New.
      </li>
      <li>
        Create username (first and last name) and enter email address.
      </li>
      <li>
        Select role and click “add new user.”
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p>User should follow instructions in confirmation email.<p>

    <p>ROLES</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Editor-in-chief should be admin</li>
      <li>Editors should be editors</li>
      <li>Writers should be authors</li>
    </ul>
